wiki.content: “That’s It” is a highly anticipated collaboration between Future and Lil Uzi Vert. Making references to their lavish lifestyle galore, the two friends rap about jewelry, drugs, and designer clothes over a guitar-led instrumental produced by Atlanta producer Wheezy. “That’s It” was heavily teased since July 2020, with multiple clips from a music video shoot. Numerous snippets of the song surfaced online over the course of the next months before the song eventually leaked in its entirety on November 10, 2020 as That’s It or Football. The music video was announced by Future on November 12, 2020, to be releasing on the same day as the album. Read more on Last.fm.
